    <section id="id22415112">
      <title>Content</title>
      <para id="id26252790">WE ARE GOING TO STUDY THE DIFFERENT TYPES OF ROCK FORMATION </para>
      <para id="id20802178">THAT FORM THE CRUST OF THE EARTH BECAUSE SEEDS DO NOT GROW EQUALLY WELL IN ALL KINDS OF SOIL.</para>
      <list id="id21458010" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Rocks, refers to the material that forms the earth's crust. Rock formations are grouped in three categories, namely igneous rocks, sedimentary rocks and metamorphic rocks. </item>
      </list>
