    <section id="id25648011">
      <title>ACTIVITY: To discuss igneous rocks as a type of rock formation [LO 2.1]</title>
      <list id="id22833632" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>These rocks are the primary, original rock formation that made up the surface of the earth.</item>
        <item>The earliest rock formations were igneous rocks that were formed when the planet started to cool down. The rocks are extremely hard and consist of several crystals.</item>
      </list>
      <figure id="id15804346">
